my welcome to @riverwheelco is out now!! so thankful for this opportunity and i can’t wait to see what we do together. this was not only hard work but so much fun to film. once again a massive thank you to @burritogueedo. I HOPE YOU ALL LIKE THE VIDEO💙 #riverwheelco #wheelsthatkeepyouflowing
iphone angle of the first clip we filmed/opening clip in my @riverwheelco welcome video. one of my favorites😋 link in bio if you haven’t watched it yet!!!

wow, so many amazing memories. over the last 7 years i have been riding for @thevaultproscootets and sadly i have made the difficult decision to leave. there is no bad blood, only love between me and everyone at the vault. i have been gifted with many amazing friends and teammates thanks to vault. i would like to thank everyone apart of the vault for their constant support, love, and belief in me. not only do i have so many great memories, but i couldn’t be more grateful that the vault help start my career and continued to help and push me throughout it. since i was 11 they have helped shape me into the person and scooter rider i am today. my first real sponsor and family. nothing but love always❤️

❤️ WELCOME TO THE TEAM ❤️ 

Say hello to the newest member of the SkatePro family @_miacatalano_ ✨ 

There is no doubt that women’s scootering is evolving, and that is because of people like Mia. She is always working hard and pushing the limits whether it’s Street or Park. She is travelling the world and killing it at all competitions - always with a big smile on her face. 

We are so excited to see what the future will bring, and we are extremely proud to have Mia on the team. LETS GO!
